snippet.title: Small Saga - Kickstarter launch trailer
snippet.description:
See the Kickstarter here: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sketchyjeremy/small-saga

Or play the demo online here: https://sketchylogic.itch.io/small-saga

What manner of vermin lurks beneath our feet? Small Saga is an RPG of miniature proportions by Jeremy Noghani.
